{"tid":775152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳茂波上月豪言已準備加碼年金發行額　今公布認購額未及半數","createTime":"2018-08-11T02:14:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-11T04:16:42.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"543845bae2be5888ce87b8b1d4f2057d7ce0f86a","tid":775152,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T02:14:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/10191950/image1533899853967.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F10191950%2Fimage1533899853967.png&h=776f2ac0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港年金計劃昨日截止認購，香港年金有限公司今日公布認購意向登記結果，首批次接獲共9,410宗登記，總認購額約49.4億港元，未及發行上限100億港元的一半。<br />\n<br />\n香港年金公司執行董事兼總裁劉應彬不認為計劃的反應冷淡，指100億或200億是風險管理限額，而非銷售目標，「如果喺限額裡面嘅任何一個嘅認購金額，我地覺得係可以接受同正常」，高於上限或會超出資本承受或管理風險的能力。<br />\n<br />\n財政司司長陳茂波曾於上月的啟動禮表示，年金計劃自公布以來，公眾反應正面，並指若獲得超額認購，公司已作好準備，將首次發行額度由100億港元提升一倍至200億港元。不過，劉應彬今日則強調「不足上限屬正常」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.post852.com/256596/%E9%99%B3%E8%8C%82%E6%B3%A2%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%88%E8%B1%AA%E8%A8%80%E5%B7%B2%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99%E5%8A%A0%E7%A2%BC%E5%B9%B4%E9%87%91%E7%99%BC%E8%A1%8C%E9%A1%8D%E3%80%80%E4%BB%8A%E5%85%AC%E5%B8%83%E8%AA%8D/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F256596%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E8%258C%2582%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%259C%2588%25E8%25B1%25AA%25E8%25A8%2580%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E6%25BA%2596%25E5%2582%2599%25E5%258A%25A0%25E7%25A2%25BC%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%2587%2591%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%25A1%258C%25E9%25A1%258D%25E3%2580%2580%25E4%25BB%258A%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25B8%2583%25E8%25AA%258D%2F&d=QBSkKEYAiAUBAIaFAeT1IDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=689bdf4f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.post852.com/256596/%E9%99%B3%E8%8C%82%E6%B3%A2%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%88%E8%B1%AA%E8%A8%80%E5%B7%B2%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99%E5%8A%A0%E7%A2%BC%E5%B9%B4%E9%87%91%E7%99%BC%E8%A1%8C%E9%A1%8D%E3%80%80%E4%BB%8A%E5%85%AC%E5%B8%83%E8%AA%8D/</a>"},{"pid":"62fbd1e336908cc2d1bc305b44acf8573523edb8","tid":775152,"uid":53588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T04:16:42.000Z","msg":"搞咁多垃圾 不如加快進度派4k"}]}